{"id":"9f930180-672f-4cf4-b9d9-9c3c08623581","title":"1498/03/28","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"e5be8e20-8c93-4094-8f5e-c5868bd151db","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"28th March. Fra Domenico preached in San Marco, saying that he was willing to pass through the fire; and he said besides that many of his companions would do the same; then turning to the women, he declared that some of them would do this also; and such was the spiritual impetus that many stood up, saying: \u0022lo sono di quelle\u0022 (I for one am ready).","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c0faff04-4508-44af-9aa1-de01139061a7","type":"tei/core/date","start":0,"end":9,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["when|1498-03-28"]},{"id":"52bd9917-1e37-4bc1-a97f-9a0d11bac756","type":"codex/time-reference","start":0,"end":9,"value":"79afa7a7-61b8-480a-be2c-1e61a320fa22","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3a0cd094-ae9b-4799-a64d-2cb69625a845","type":"page","start":0,"end":348,"value":"134","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"75d47011-0660-4705-a45d-13c982fb5fad","type":"style/superscript","start":2,"end":3,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"166db214-9baa-49c8-aa0f-d4bc8bdc22c8","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":23,"value":"cbc641b0-3aa0-4f2a-99ff-49a0193a43ff","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e7c43890-ef78-4c6a-8c9e-c1f291f0704c","type":"style/italics","start":37,"end":45,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"42e6d8ca-1a7d-419c-9291-9e2673b7b970","type":"language","start":37,"end":45,"value":"it","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ccadbb2a-064b-4a82-bdae-b9605228e564","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":37,"end":45,"value":"36624084-7614-4020-b1e5-f62478667769","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"18f968ce-8421-4436-a6de-4bcd88bcb5a3","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":60,"end":61,"value":"cbc641b0-3aa0-4f2a-99ff-49a0193a43ff","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"81b4846f-973b-4808-8182-c8372c40be64","type":